The paper deals with graph theory and specifically the Flat Wall Theorem, which is a result in structural graph theory. The paper provides improved bounds for the theorem and also discusses the low-degree scenario. This suggests that the paper is likely to be categorized under Discrete Mathematics (cs.DM), Computational Geometry (cs.CG), Graph Theory (cs.GT), Data Structures and Algorithms (cs.DS), and Computational Complexity (cs.CC).
